{
  "stem": "8916.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No-- no Nazi would ever do a thing like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he'd speak to me and my brother, who also worked on the next machine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- the following day, I would find out that he ordered a special ration of-- an extra ration of soup for me, something like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Just these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But eventually the-- so that gives you an idea of what Schindler-- how Schindler was acting in relation to his Jewish workers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Each--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my-- specially my family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm sure that everyone on Schindler's company-- in Schindler's company had a personal story like this to tell, where Schindler acted in a human fashion rather than the Nazi fashion.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so eventually the war for the Germans went bad in the Eastern Front, and the-- the Russians were advancing, and these companies were going to be liquidated.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister's company had actually closed, and all the workers were sent back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But Schindler decided that he would-- he would not let his-- his workers simply go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He would-- he was going to transfer his company-- lock, stock, and barrel-- over to Czechoslovakia and move his Jewish workers with him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was a pretty outlandish or preposterous kind of suggestion, really.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All these experts were-- had to be transferred with the company.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he managed to do all this with-- by bribing people and by his fast talking and whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not in so many words.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But why he was moving the company was simply so that he would have someplace for us to-- to move to.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In any case, he-- we did move the company.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and the men were then sent back, temporarily, to Plaszow, back to this main camp, and as well as the women.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
